OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776906184
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record level as UK
OL,4,Cpopulation ages
OL,6,FCancer cases have reached a record
OL,7,Flevel in the UK, with around one
OL,8,Fperson diagnosed every 80 seconds,
OL,9,Ffigures suggest.
OL,11,FAnalysis by Cancer Research UK shows
OL,12,Fmore than 403,000 people are diagnosed
OL,13,Fwith the disease every year, largely
OL,14,Fdue to a growing and ageing
OL,15,Fpopulation, with people more likely to
OL,16,Fdevelop the disease as they age.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
