FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776906184
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record level as UK
OL,4,Cpopulation ages
OL,6,FThe charity warned that NHS services
OL,7,Fare struggling to cope with rising
OL,8,Fdemand, with cancer waiting times
OL,9,Facross the UK among the worst on
OL,10,Frecord.
OL,12,FIts new Cancer in the UK Report 2026
OL,13,Fshows incidences have risen to 620 per
OL,14,F100,000 people in a decade (from 610),
OL,15,Fwhile cases diagnosed at an early
OL,16,Fstage have barely changed (from 54% to
OL,17,F55%).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
