CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776906184
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record level as UK
OL,4,Cpopulation ages
OL,6,FDeath rates have fallen and the
OL,7,Fproportion of people surviving a
OL,8,Fdecade or more has risen, but Cancer
OL,9,FResearch UK said this progress is at
OL,10,Frisk of stalling, in part due to
OL,11,Fpressure on cancer services.
OL,13,FIt said the Government's recently
OL,14,Fpublished National Cancer Plan for
OL,15,FEngland is a "crucial step" towards
OL,16,Fimproving care, but there needs to be
OL,17,F"funding and resources to translate
OL,18,Fambition into impact".
OL,26,@wD@NOUwD@[O]yD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
