CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776906184
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record level as UK
OL,4,Cpopulation ages
OL,6,FMichelle Mitchell, Cancer Research
OL,7,FUK's chief executive, said: "More
OL,8,Fpeople are being diagnosed with cancer
OL,9,Fthan ever before.
OL,11,F"Although cancer survival has doubled
OL,12,Fsince the 1970s, progress has slowed
OL,13,Fover the last decade.
OL,15,F"The UK Government's recently
OL,16,Fpublished National Cancer Plan for
OL,17,FEngland could make a big difference,
OL,18,Fbut only if it turns into improvements
OL,19,Ffor cancer patients.
OL,26,@oD@]OUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776906184
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record level as UK
OL,4,Cpopulation ages
OL,6,F"Publishing the plan is not a 'job
OL,7,Fdone' on cancer: ambitions to diagnose
OL,8,Fcancers earlier, meet cancer wait
OL,9,Ftargets and improve best practice
OL,10,Ftreatment must happen quickly."
OL,12,FThe charity wants screening programmes
OL,13,Fsuch as for lung cancer to be rolled
OL,14,Fout widely and effectively and the
OL,15,Frollout of innovative cancer tests to
OL,16,Fbe accelerated.
OL,18,FAround 107,000 cancer patients were
OL,19,Fwaiting more than 62 days to start
OL,20,Ftreatment across the UK in 2025, it
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
