OL,3,CCancer cases reach record level as UK
OL,4,Cpopulation ages
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We have delivered
OL,8,Fa record number of diagnostic tests in
OL,9,Fthe last 12 months, backed by an extra
OL,10,F#26 billion for the NHS ` and the
OL,11,Fnumber of patients getting a cancer
OL,12,Fdiagnosis or all-clear on time is the
OL,13,Fhighest in five years ` but we are not
OL,14,Fcomplacent.
OL,26,@oD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
