FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776906184
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record level as UK
OL,4,Cpopulation ages
OL,6,F"Our National Cancer Plan sets out how
OL,7,Fpatients will receive a diagnosis
OL,8,Ffaster, treatment sooner and better
OL,9,Fsupport to live well with cancer, with
OL,10,Fthe aim of 75% of patients diagnosed
OL,11,Ffrom 2035 to be cancer-free or living
OL,12,Fwell after five years.
OL,14,F"Our historic Tobacco and Vapes Bill,
OL,15,Fwhich is due to come into law soon,
OL,16,Fwill also protect future generations
OL,17,Ffrom cancer."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
