OL,3,CCancer cases reach record level as UK
OL,4,Cpopulation ages
OL,6,FNatalia Norori, head of data and
OL,7,Fevidence at Prostate Cancer UK, said:
OL,8,F"Cancer diagnoses are rising, and as
OL,9,Fthe UK's most common cancer, with
OL,10,F64,000 new cases each year, prostate
OL,11,Fcancer plays a big part in this.
OL,13,F"The good news is that prostate cancer
OL,14,Fis highly treatable when caught early.
OL,16,F"But with more than 1,000,000 men set
OL,17,Fto be living with the disease by 2040,
OL,18,Fearly detection needs to be a priority
OL,19,Fif we're serious about saving lives."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776906184
OL,3,CCancer cases reach record level as UK
OL,4,Cpopulation ages
OL,6,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "Latest data
OL,7,Fshows that early diagnosis in England
OL,8,Fis at a record high and is continuing
OL,9,Fto rise, with staff also now
OL,10,Fdelivering 30% more cancer checks than
OL,11,Fin 2021 ` ensuring survival is also at
OL,12,Fan all-time high.
OL,14,F"But we know we need to go further to
OL,15,Fdiagnose more cancers earlier and save
OL,16,Fmore lives, which is why the National
OL,17,FCancer Plan will transform services to
OL,18,Fspeed up diagnosis, cut waits and
OL,19,Fimprove care for anyone affected."
OL,26,@nD@[OUvD@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
